des:
Outlets Williamsburg’s skill will let you know all the important information and happenings at the center. Whether you’re curious what type of stores they have, when they will be closing, or what the next upcoming event is, download this skill to be informed on all things at Outlets Williamsburg. 

To get started, enable Outlets Williamsburg’s skill through the Alexa App or by saying, “Alexa, open Outlets Williamsburg.”

If you’re having trouble, please visit www.outletswilliamsburg.com.
